Jose Mourinho has landed a provocative blow ahead of Sunday's Stamford Bridge clash with Arsenal, claiming Cesc Fabregas already ‘loves Chelsea’ and has ‘no regrets’ about returning to a different part of London.

Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger has claimed his former star’s priority was a summer move back to the Emirates from Barcelona.

